   /*            Creation Date - 08/09/1997                          */
   /*      Last Amendment Date -   /  /                              */
   /*----------------------------------------------------------------*/
   /*  Purpose                                                       */
   /*  ~~~~~~~                                                       */
   /*  Slow X7PF access for TMENU routines                           */
   /*----------------------------------------------------------------*/
   /*  Change Control                                                */
   /*  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~                                                */
   /*  Date            Initials      Amendment                       */
   /*  ~~~~            ~~~~~~~~      ~~~~~~~~~                       */
